Nearby, a cybersecurity company presents a password cracking challenge on a laptop, and healthcare providers showcase community outreach photos, highlighting the connection between technology and community service. A whiteboard features employers scheduling same-day interviews, fostering interaction for job seekers. Monitors by the exit display a post-event survey link. Outside the university gym, students line up before the career fair opens, and as they exit, they carry tote bags and stacks of business cards while comparing swag items such as water bottles and phone chargers. Groups of friends mark target employers on the event map, and after the event, volunteers stack collapsed booths and gather leftover brochures while small groups analyze which recruiters seemed most enthusiastic.
